measurements.description: Two hundred seventy-six flowers and 516 buds on 12 inflorescences up to 32cm in length; sepals and petals chartreuse boldly marked dark cordovan coalescent blotches; lip yellow-green sidelobes overlaid brown stripes fusing to solid distally, midlobe yellow overlaid brown basally, bright yellow distally; column light green weakly overlaid brown spots, anther cap yellow; substance firm; texture matte.
